metadata.name: Urban Daydream 1, 2019
metadata.description:
Winter Sun during the afternoon at the Rotterdam train station. Netherlands, 2019.

Edition: 1 / 1

Collection: Urban Daydreams

‘Urban Daydreams’ is a series of photographs taken in different cities of Brazil, Finland and Netherlands. It explores human interactions that unfold inside urban areas and their geometrical spaces and it was exhibited for the first time in 2020.

Includes: One 30 x 20 cm archival quality print and worldwide delivery free of charge (for first time buyer only).
